Apprs: CO: SRN, Rpr: Kasten, Clerk: Evenson. ADA: Edward Minser with ADA Mike Nieskes DF ATTY:  Daniel P Repka DF: Anthony Nmi Partee appeared from jail. Case called at 8:48. Includes 15CF134, 15CF135. Atty. Repka updates the court. ADA Nieskes responds. Court reads charge and maximum penalty. DE pleads G to 15CF134 amended to misdemeanor battery and G to 15CF135 amended to misdemeanor battery.  DE sworn. Crt reviews plea questionnaire and informs DE of rights. Crt finds DE freely, voluntarily and knowingly waives rights and makes plea. Attorney's stipulate to the facts. Crt accepts plea, finds factual basis and finds DE guilty of 15CF134 and 15CF135 amending both to misdemeanor battery. Sentencing arguments. Court takes judicial notice of 14CF465. DE is currently in Waupun. Crt orders:
On 15CF134 
- 9 months jail to be served concurrent with DE present prison sentence
- Costs of $243.00
- Submit DNA sample and pay surcharge of $200.00
- Restitution to the St. Croix County Jail of $497.00.

On 15CF135
- 9 months jail to be served concurrent with 15CF134 and concurrent to DE prision sentence. 
- Costs of $243.00
- Submit DNA sample and pay surcharge of $200.00
- Restitution to the St. Croix County jail of $464.17. 

Court extends 10 days for Atty. Repka to file a motion formally heard. 
Court will convert all costs to a civil judgment.
Filed by Atty Repka. Re: attached letter and request for plea date. km
